    "encrypted": "false",
    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "### Random Block\r\n\r\nPenny used `play random` to choose different beat tracks as the song played. Let's try to make the bass and lead tracks random as well:\r\n\r\n1) Drag a <code style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 148, 202); color: white; border: none; box-shadow: inset -1px -1px 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5), inset 1px 1px 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.8); padding: 4px\">play random</code> block inside the second `repeat` loop. [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-id:play_random_toolbox---id:repeat_workspace_1)\r\n2) Move the <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-boombox\" style=\"color: #58BEF9; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Bass </span> track inside, then add two more tracks [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-id:play_toolbox---id:repeat_workspace_1)\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/cec44314121a7784b6e127f3e3113976-image-1751981482218.png)\r\n\r\n3) Drag another <code style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 148, 202); color: white; border: none; box-shadow: inset -1px -1px 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5), inset 1px 1px 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.8); padding: 4px\">play random</code> block inside the third `repeat` loop. [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-id:play_random_toolbox---id:repeat_workspace_2)\r\n4) Move the <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-guitars\" style=\"color: #64D25A; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Lead </span> track inside, then add two more tracks [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-id:play_toolbox---id:repeat_workspace_2)\r\n\r\nPress the <code style=\"background-color: #fca401; color: white; border: none; box-shadow: inset -1px -1px 1px1 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5), inset 1px 1px 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.8); padding: 4px\">Run</code> button! You should a different selection of beat, bass, and lead tracks as the song plays!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/72853e7ec0dd384e1d5699a2398ac7e0-image-1745344961777.png)\r\n\r\n",
    "offer_browser_tts": "true",
    "use_secondary_finish_button": "false",
    "hide_share_and_remix": "true",
